metadata.name: ANIPANG SUPPORTER #0001
metadata.description: ANIPANG SUPPORTER CLUB is a project that gives $BLUE PAW to supporters as ANIPANG PNE games grow. (with no need to play!) Original ANIPANG is a high-quality casual game with 100 Million+ downloads, and it’s known as ‘K-Candy Crush’. Holders can get access to Game-based Mint Pass that will be launched later.
